---
title: Cheesy Mediterranean Style Chickpea Pie with Aubergine, Pepper and Herby Carrots
description: Pies are comforting and perfect for winter, plus they don't need meat to be a real comfort food. Here, we're heroing chickpeas alongside Mediterranean style veg for a delicious veggie meal.
